# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:15
translate spanish hwb_s08_3bad69f1:

    # "A thunderous banging wakes me from a dead sleep, rattling the entire motorhome."
    "Un golpe ensordecedor me despierta de un sueño profundo, sacudiendo toda la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:18
translate spanish hwb_s08_d59e2aa9:

    # "{color=#ffdab3}???{/color}" "{size=+10}HEY! {w=0.8}I KNOW YOU TWO ARE IN THERE! {w=0.8}YOU THIEVES BETTER NOT STILL BE SLEEPING!{/size}" with hpunch
    "{color=#ffdab3}???{/color}" "{size=+10}ЭЙ! {w=0.8}Я ЗНАЮ ЧТО ВЫ СЕЙЧАС ТАМ! {w=0.8}ДЛЯ ВАШЕГО ЖЕ БЛАГА НАДЕЮСЬ ВЫ ДВОЕ ВОРИШЕК НЕ СПИТЕ!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:20
translate spanish hwb_s08_09a44c72:

    # "The muffled shout leaks in from outside, followed by another voice."
    "El grito amortiguado se filtra desde afuera, seguido de otra voz."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:23
translate spanish hwb_s08_adcf3120:

    # "{color=#c9c9c9}???{/color}" "Sis, it’s not even seven. Can I go back to bed?"
    "{color=#c9c9c9}???{/color}\" \"Hermana, ni siquiera son las siete. ¿Puedo volver a la cama?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:25
translate spanish hwb_s08_cb0261a6:

    # "And another voice."
    "Y otra voz."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:28
translate spanish hwb_s08_54733566:

    # "{color=#FF9201}???{/color}" "You’re better off just rolling with it. For her, it may as well be noon."
    "{color=#FF9201}???{/color}\" \"Es mejor que te dejes llevar. Para ella, bien podría ser mediodía."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:31
translate spanish hwb_s08_1987da9f:

    # "{color=#ffdab3}???{/color}" "{size=+10}OPEN UP OR I SWEAR JOE'S GONNA BUST DOWN THIS DOOR!{/size}"
    "{color=#ffdab3}???{/color}\" \"{size=+10}¡ABRE O JURÓ POR JOE QUE VA A DERRIBAR ESTA PUERTA!{/size}"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s08_107dd90c:

    # "{color=#FF9201}???{/color}" "Wait, what."
    "{color=#FF9201}???{/color}\" \"Espera, ¿qué?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:36
translate spanish hwb_s08_80857e32:

    # "Gee, I wonder who this could be?"
    "Vaya, me pregunto quién podría ser."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s08_ac09f052:

    # "I roll out of bed and open the slider connecting to the other ‘rooms.’"
    "Me levanto de la cama y abro la puerta corrediza que conecta con las otras \"habitaciones\"."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s08_b430dc66:

    # "Marina is sitting pressed up against the back of the foldout bed with the sheets over her head."
    "Marina está sentada, apretada contra el respaldo de la cama plegable, con las sábanas sobre la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s08_53d44639:

    # Marina "Who do you think it is?"
    Marina "Как думаешь, кто это?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:74
translate spanish hwb_s08_f5f69a2c:

    # Amber "Take a wild guess."
    Amber "А ты догадайся."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:85
translate spanish hwb_s08_86b97a98:

    # "I march over and throw open the door. As expected, my three favorite people stand before me."
    "Marcho hacia allá y abro la puerta de golpe. Como era de esperar, mis tres personas favoritas están frente a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s08_2db15ad0:

    # Mariah "It’s about time. Do you have any idea how long we’ve been out here?"
    Mariah "Да неужели. Ты хоть представляешь, сколько мы тут ждали?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s08_90160139:

    # "A groggy Tess sways from side to side. Joseph’s gentle hands are the only thing preventing her from passing out on the ground."
    "Una Tess somnolienta se balancea de un lado a otro. Las manos suaves de Joseph son lo único que evita que se desmaye en el suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s08_04c14add:

    # Amber "It’s funny that {i}you{/i} of all people accuse {i}us{/i} of theft."
    Amber "Забавно, что из всех людей {i}ты{/i} обвиняешь {i}нас{/i} в краже."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s08_d43d7fb7:

    # Mariah "What else would you call what happened to my equipment?"
    Mariah "А как еще назвать то, что вы сделали с моим оборудованием?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s08_b5de1b68:

    # Amber "I don’t know? ‘Borrowing?’ You loaned it to us, remember?"
    Amber "Даже не знаю? “Одалживание?” Ты одолжила его нам, помнишь?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s08_5a82bb43:

    # Mariah "Correction—Joe loaned it to you."
    Mariah "Поправочка – Джо одолжил его вам."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s08_07f6263b:

    # "Joseph gives a tired smirk and a wave."
    "Joseph sonríe cansadamente y saluda con la mano."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s08_4fd8d1ee:

    # Mariah "I was forced to sit idly by and watch you make off with it. That’s theft if I’ve ever seen it."
    Mariah "Я была вынуждена сидеть сложа руки и смотреть, как вы удираете с ним. Это ни что иное, как кража."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s08_38000a7a:

    # "She pushes me aside and clambers into the motorhome, followed by the other two."
    "Me empuja a un lado y se sube a la casa rodante, seguida por los otros dos."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s08_bcc485f5:

    # Joseph "Looks like we’re coming in."
    Joseph "Похоже, что мы все-таки зайдем."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s08_412ccbcf:

    # Tess "Good morning."
    Tess "Доброе утро."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s08_8bce8333:

    # Marina "Hey, you three! Morning! How’re you guys doing?"
    Marina "Эй, троица! Доброе утро! Как вы, ребята, поживаете?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s08_4809cccc:

    # Joseph "Tired. For what it’s worth, we tried stopping her."
    Joseph "Устали. Мы изо всех сил пытались ее остановить."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s08_5de796bd:

    # "Mariah stomps to the middle of the motorhome, analyzing everything before releasing a loud scoff."
    "Mariah camina pisando fuerte hasta el centro de la casa rodante, analizándolo todo antes de soltar una fuerte risa burlona."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:186
translate spanish hwb_s08_ec9ac505:

    # Mariah "So where’s my stuff?"
    Mariah "Ну и где мое оборудование?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s08_68902992:

    # Amber "If you don’t get out of my RV in five seconds, it’ll be shoved up your a—"
    Amber "Если ты не уберешься из моего трейлера в течение пяти секунд, то я запихну это оборудование тебе—"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:198
translate spanish hwb_s08_e36838dc:

    # Marina "Don’t worry about it, you guys are great."
    Marina "Ой, да не беспокойтесь об этом. Вы, ребята, клевые."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s08_a2aed2c0:

    # Marina "Hey Tess, did you hang up your new windchime?"
    Marina "Эй, Тесс, ты повесила свою музыкальную подвеску?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s08_880e7f4c:

    # "Tess’ eyes flicker with interest for all of a second then return to their obstinate droopy state."
    "Los ojos de Tess brillan con interés por un segundo y luego vuelven a su estado obstinadamente somnoliento."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s08_da5bcd5e:

    # Tess "Uh-huh. Above my bed."
    Tess "Ага. Над кроватью."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s08_adce9750:

    # Mariah "What’s up with the foldout? You two don’t sleep together?"
    Mariah "А чего это у вас раскладушка разложена? Вы двое не спите вместе?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s08_8ea336b1:

    # "{color=#ee320f}Amber{/color} & {color=#ffd200}Marina{/color}" "Wh-What?!"
    AmberMarina "Чт-Что?!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s08_2cfdae62:

    # Joseph "Told ya."
    Joseph "А я тебе говорил."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s08_1b712e7e:

    # Mariah "Dammit."
    Mariah "Проклятье."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s08_7b132f83:

    # "Grumbling, Mariah pulls a bill from her pocket and slaps it in Joe’s hand."
    "Refunfuñando, Mariah saca un billete de su bolsillo y lo golpea en la mano de Joe."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s08_215aa86e:

    # Tess "Does that mean we get to sleep in tomorrow morning?"
    Tess "Это значит, что мы будем отсыпаться следующим утром?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s08_d11580de:

    # Joseph "Sure does, kiddo. Sure does."
    Joseph "Конечно, малышка. Несомненно."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s08_108da190:

    # "The ringleader of the circus returns to inspecting the motorhome, fiddling with the magnets on the fridge."
    "La líder del circo vuelve a inspeccionar la casa rodante, jugueteando con los imanes en el refrigerador."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s08_12920dde:

    # Mariah "Anyway, give me back my equipment and we’ll get out of your hair."
    Mariah "В общем, отдай нам наше оборудование и мы исчезнем."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s08_9a396afe:

    # Joseph "C’mon, just let them use it. It’s the least we can do after tearing apart her car."
    Joseph "Да ладно тебе, пусть пользуются. Это меньшее, что мы можем сделать после того, как разобрали ее машину."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s08_09ae4fda:

    # "Mariah's attention turns to the counter, topped with the opened box of stunning, gold nuggets from the night before."
    "La atención de Mariah se dirige al mostrador, cubierto con la caja abierta de los impresionantes pepitas de oro de anoche."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s08_e794ffaf:

    # Mariah "And who’s fault was tha—"
    Mariah "А чья это была вин—"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s08_5bf967de:

    # Mariah "What is this?"
    Mariah "Что это?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s08_bd732e32:

    # Amber "What is what?"
    Amber "Где?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s08_5d073eae:

    # Mariah "The thing on the counter. It almost looks like…"
    Mariah "Там на подставке. Выглядит почти как…"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s08_6e356178:

    # Marina "Oh, that?"
    Marina "А, ты про это?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s08_4f7a9fcd:

    # Marina "That’s the piece of the treasure we found!"
    Marina "Это часть сокровища, которую мы нашли!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s08_7822850a:

    # Mariah "Hah! Yeah right. You’re kidding."
    Mariah "Ха! Ну конечно. Ты прикалываешься."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s08_4b18fd90:

    # "She chuckles."
    "Ella se ríe entre dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:289
translate spanish hwb_s08_0764ef52:

    # "She stops."
    "Se detiene."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s08_8e66e43b:

    # Mariah "She is kidding, right?"
    Mariah "Она ведь не серьезно, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s08_6099c15c:

    # "I have a devious thought, and crack an equally devious smile."
    "Tengo un pensamiento malvado, y esbozo una sonrisa igualmente malvada."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s08_f169cc6a:

    # Amber "Nope. She’s telling the truth. One-hundred percent."
    Amber "Еще как серьезно. Это правда. На сто процентов."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s08_9d31058d:

    # "I wrap my arm around Mariah and bring her close. Joseph and Tess shoot each other alarmed glances."
    "Rodeo a Mariah con el brazo y la acerco. Joseph y Tess intercambian miradas alarmadas."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s08_368e0213:

    # Amber "We found it last night—with your equipment."
    Amber "Мы нашли это прошлой ночью с помощью твоего оборудования."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s08_c15158b4:

    # "She stands there, stupefied."
    "Ella se queda ahí, estupefacta."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s08_92167525:

    # Mariah "N-No. That’s impossible. You’re lying!"
    Mariah "Н-нет. Невозможно. Вы все врете!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s08_0fcefeba:

    # Amber "Really now?"
    Amber "Неужели?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s08_fbb6a929:

    # Amber "Hey Marina, why don’t you tell her about it?"
    Amber "Эй, Марина, почему бы тебе не рассказать ей все?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s08_a9c1f36f:

    # Marina "Sure thing!"
    Marina "Конечно!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s08_7f0da712:

    # Marina "It started yesterday after we met. Amber looked at the journal again and thought that it might be near the smaller rocks behind the bigger one. They’re called dikes, I think."
    Marina "Все началось вчера после нашей встречи. Эмбер снова посмотрела в дневник и подумала, что сокровище могло быть рядом с более мелкими скалами за более крупной горой. Их называют дайками, я полагаю."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s08_024a5970:

    # Marina "Anyway, turns out she was right!"
    Marina "Короче, выходит она была права!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s08_cb9c90c7:

    # "Mariah looks down, muttering to herself."
    "Mariah mira hacia abajo, murmurando para sí misma."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s08_2e797a91:

    # Mariah "But how…"
    Mariah "Но как…"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s08_673727e9:

    # Mariah "Why wouldn’t he just hide it on the mountain…?"
    Mariah "Почему он не спрятал его просто на горе…?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s08_1e7ea1d0:

    # Mariah "It doesn’t make sense... If he was going back to Missouri..."
    Mariah "Это не имеет смысла... Если он собирался возвращаться в Миссури..."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s08_5109ef25:

    # "Her voice diminishes, until her words are reduced to lip flaps. Like a mad scientist trying to figure out a complex equation, she retreats into her own little world."
    "Su voz se desvanece, hasta que sus palabras se reducen a movimientos de labios. Como una científica loca tratando de resolver una ecuación compleja, se retira a su propio pequeño mundo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:358
translate spanish hwb_s08_dfeb99f2:

    # Marina "M-Mariah?"
    Marina "Ма-Мария?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s08_72008ce4:

    # "A smidge of sympathy buds inside me. I look to Joseph and Tess. Even they look a little shocked."
    "Un poco de compasión brota dentro de mí. Miro a Joseph y Tess. Incluso ellos parecen un poco impactados."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:364
translate spanish hwb_s08_d4d98a26:

    # Amber "Is she gonna be okay?"
    Amber "С ней все нормально?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s08_f398e39d:

    # Joseph "I… honestly don’t know."
    Joseph "Я… если честно, не знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s08_f0e1abd4:

    # "Tess approaches Mariah, who is still whispering nonsense under her breath. Nonchalantly, Tess hops in front of her, her hand reaching upwards, trying to wave it in front of Mariah and bring her back to our world."
    "Tess se acerca a Mariah, que todavía susurra tonterías en voz baja. Con despreocupación, Tess salta frente a ella, su mano se eleva, tratando de agitarla frente a Mariah y traerla de vuelta a nuestro mundo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s08_77d65967:

    # "No response."
    "Sin respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s08_c7f8422c:

    # "Tess pulls Mariah's arms skyward, then allows them to flop down to her side."
    "Tess levanta los brazos de Mariah hacia el cielo, luego los deja caer a sus costados."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:400
translate spanish hwb_s08_a501a202:

    # "Still no response."
    "Aún sin respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s08_6968857d:

    # Joseph "You know, we’ve been looking into that treasure since we were kids."
    Joseph "Знаете, мы искали это сокровище с детства."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s08_1119f0e0:

    # "Joseph steps up to the counter and stares into the box."
    "Joseph se acerca al mostrador y mira fijamente dentro de la caja."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s08_987e1171:

    # Joseph "Never expected someone else to find it before us."
    Joseph "Никогда не думал, что кто-либо найдет его раньше нас."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s08_d5afbf2d:

    # Amber "That’s more than I can say. I didn’t even think it existed."
    Amber "А я тем более. Я даже не думала, что оно существует."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:419
translate spanish hwb_s08_cc6c583b:

    # Joseph "There’s that too."
    Joseph "И это тоже."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s08_0fb08836:

    # "He sighs. Then, with a shrug, cracks a smile."
    "Suspira. Luego, con un encogimiento de hombros, esboza una sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:425
translate spanish hwb_s08_1bb8d648:

    # Joseph "Well, good job anyway. You ladies seem cool, so if it couldn’t be us then at least it was you."
    Joseph "Что ж, в любом случае, хорошая работа. Вы, леди, кажетесь клевыми, поэтому если не мы, то лучше вы."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:429
translate spanish hwb_s08_4ba1475a:

    # Marina "You guys wanna stick around? We could tell you more about it."
    Marina "Вы, ребята, еще хотите здесь послоняться? Мы бы могли вам рассказать побольше."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:431
translate spanish hwb_s08_5134ca0a:

    # "He looks at Mariah."
    "Mira a Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:435
translate spanish hwb_s08_4dd66c25:

    # Joseph "Somehow, I don’t think that would be healthy for her—or you."
    Joseph "Что-то не уверен, что это будет безопасно для вас обеих."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:437
translate spanish hwb_s08_4c599e22:

    # "He grabs Mariah by the shoulders and begins pushing her towards the exit."
    "Toma a Mariah por los hombros y comienza a empujarla hacia la salida."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s08_8510866f:

    # Joseph "C’mon Mariah, let’s go make you a nice, cold michelada."
    Joseph "Давай, Мария, пойдем сделаем тебе хорошую кружечку прохладной мичелады."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s08_0e2cb6fc:

    # Joseph "You two can keep the equipment. Think of it as an apology gift."
    Joseph "Вы двое можете оставить оборудование себе. Пусть это будет подарком в качестве извинений."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s08_eca4953c:

    # "Because cheaply made tools I could get at any hardware store are of equal value to a car."
    "Porque herramientas baratas que podría conseguir en cualquier ferretería tienen el mismo valor que un auto."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s08_593ce9b8:

    # "They’re almost out of the motorhome, when Mariah flips and rushes back."
    "Están casi fuera de la casa rodante, cuando Mariah da la vuelta y regresa corriendo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s08_5921513f:

    # Mariah "{size=+10}HOLD ON A MINUTE, THIEF!{/size}" with hpunch
    Mariah "{size=+10}ОДНУ МИНУТУ, ВОРЮГА!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s08_c65a610b:

    # "She looks me straight in the eyes, her expression returning to that of a piercing hawk."
    "Me mira directamente a los ojos, su expresión volviendo a ser la de un halco penetrante."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s08_91790c28:

    # Mariah "You just had beginner's luck."
    Mariah "Новичкам просто везет."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s08_2e2eb18c:

    # Mariah "You might’ve found the first piece, but I promise you: me and my team will find the rest."
    Mariah "Может быть, вы и нашли первую часть, но обещаю вам: я и мои друзья найдем все остальные."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s08_7f344e25:

    # "She extends a hand and smirks."
    "Extiende una mano y sonríe con suficiencia."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s08_00976864:

    # "I pause for a moment, then grab it and offer a smirk of my own."
    "Me detengo un momento, luego la tomo y ofrezco mi propia sonrisa burlona."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s08_cd4c437e:

    # Amber "You’re on."
    Amber "Это мы еще посмотрим."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:494
translate spanish hwb_s08_3fa8d933:

    # "Marina and Joseph both let out a sigh of relief, as if they’ve just witnessed the signing of a peace treaty."
    "Marina y Joseph ambos suspiran aliviados, como si acabaran de presenciar la firma de un tratado de paz."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s08_e0bfdcb9:

    # Joseph "Well, guess that takes care of that."
    Joseph "Что ж, думаю, беспокоиться не о чем."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s08_0ce00e0b:

    # Mariah "Now let’s get out of here and go back to a proper base."
    Mariah "А теперь давайте убираться отсюда и возвращаться к поискам."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:508
translate spanish hwb_s08_663ae9ba:

    # Tess "Are you going to drink until you feel better again, sis?"
    Tess "Ты собираешься пить, пока тебе не станет лучше, сестренка?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:510
translate spanish hwb_s08_50029ef3:

    # Mariah "Sh-Shut up! Didn’t Mom ever teach you any manners?"
    Mariah "Зат-Заткнись! Мама разве не научила тебе манерам?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:514
translate spanish hwb_s08_a18e1c42:

    # Tess "You always said Mom is an airheaded ditz who wouldn’t know good advice or a good man if it bit her on the butt."
    Tess "Ты всегда говорила, что мама легкомысленная дурочка, которая не распознала бы хорошего совета или достойного человека, пока он не укусит ее за задницу."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:516
translate spanish hwb_s08_aa23bede:

    # Mariah "Oh yeah."
    Mariah "Ах да."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:522
translate spanish hwb_s08_99bce579:

    # Joseph "Sorry for all the trouble, ladies. See you two down the road."
    Joseph "Простите за все неудобства, дамы. Еще увидимся."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s08_90ca028a:

    # "Joseph pulls the door closed. Marina and I stay put, as the bickering of the trio fades into the distance."
    "Joseph cierra la puerta. Marina y yo nos quedamos quietas, mientras las discusiones del trío se desvanecen en la distancia."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:537
translate spanish hwb_s08_540b63fe:

    # Marina "Were you serious?"
    Marina "Ты говорила серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s08_74d49bca:

    # Amber "Hm? About what?"
    Amber "А? О чем?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s08_f86c27ca:

    # Marina "The treasure. You told Mariah that you were gonna find the rest."
    Marina "О сокровище. Ты сказала Марие, что собираешься найти остальные части."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:549
translate spanish hwb_s08_c172a28f:

    # Marina "If you were just being nice and wanna leave now, that’s fine too. You’ve already done a lot for me."
    Marina "Если это было просто из вежливости и на самом деле ты хочешь уехать, то все нормально. Ты и так уже много для меня сделала."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:553
translate spanish hwb_s08_ea33f0b4:

    # "She casts her eyes downwards to hide her emotions, but I know better by now."
    "Baja la mirada para ocultar sus emociones, pero yo ya la conozco mejor."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:559
translate spanish hwb_s08_6a67e787:

    # Amber "And let you keep all the treasure for yourself? Hell no!"
    Amber "И позволить тебе забрать все сокровище себе? Черта с два!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:563
translate spanish hwb_s08_9df31617:

    # "Her eyes bounce back."
    "Sus ojos se elevan de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:565
translate spanish hwb_s08_950bc97d:

    # Amber "Besides, someone’s gotta keep you from getting yourself into trouble."
    Amber "К тому же кто-то должен проследить, чтобы ты ни во что не вляпалась."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:569
translate spanish hwb_s08_66985f89:

    # Amber "May as well be me."
    Amber "Этим кем-то могу быть и я."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s08_c182cc7a:

    # Marina "For real? But don’t you have the festival to go to?"
    Marina "Правда? Но разве тебе не нужно на фестиваль?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:577
translate spanish hwb_s08_b2303175:

    # Amber "Eh, it’s still a little while away. I wanted to do some sight seeing anyway."
    Amber "Да он все равно еще не скоро. Я хотела посмотреть на какие-нибудь достопримечательности перед этим."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:579
translate spanish hwb_s08_05f78dd1:

    # "Marina launches forward."
    "Marina se lanza hacia adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:581
translate spanish hwb_s08_d945749f:

    # "Before I can sidestep, she tackles me with the force of a gold-filled freight train."
    "Antes de que pueda esquivarla, me embiste con la fuerza de un tren de carga lleno de oro."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:594
translate spanish hwb_s08_ede06fed:

    # "I don’t even try to resist. It’s futile in the grace of Marina’s hugs."
    "Ni siquiera intento resistirme. Es inútil ante la gracia de los abrazos de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:598
translate spanish hwb_s08_b603a1e6:

    # Marina "Thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you thank you!"
    Marina "Спасибо спасибо спасибо спасибо спасибо спасибо спасибо!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:602
translate spanish hwb_s08_d0c2467a:

    # Amber "Actually, I probably owe you an apology."
    Amber "Ну вообще-то, я, вероятно, должна извиниться."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:606
translate spanish hwb_s08_8f98f266:

    # "She cocks her head and looks up at me. I look away, my bashful side taking over."
    "Inclina la cabeza y me mira. Yo desvío la mirada, dejando que mi lado tímido tome el control."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:608
translate spanish hwb_s08_b6a6e3f3:

    # Amber "Well… you know. I kept saying it wasn’t real and stuff…"
    Amber "Ну… знаешь. Я твердила, что его не существует и все такое…"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:612
translate spanish hwb_s08_9a35875b:

    # Marina "Hey, don’t worry about it. Most people wouldn’t have even given me the time of day."
    Marina "Эй, да не переживай ты об этом. Большинство людей не дали бы мне и шанса."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:614
translate spanish hwb_s08_b610ac08:

    # Amber "Yeah, but…"
    Amber "Да, но…"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:618
translate spanish hwb_s08_daf381b6:

    # Marina "Relaaaaax. Just figure out where have to go next."
    Marina "Расслааабься. Просто выясни, куда идти дальше."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:624
translate spanish hwb_s08_ad10a89a:

    # "I smile."
    "Sonrío."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s08_0a334665:

    # "We walk to the front of the R.V. and take our seats. Grabbing the journal from the glove department, I flip it open."
    "Caminamos al frente de la casa rodante y tomamos asiento. Tomando el diario de la guantera, lo abro."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:640
translate spanish hwb_s08_c58685a0:

    # "I glance over the second to last entry. Key phrases like ‘split path,’ ‘detour,’ and ‘acres of identical arched stone’ throw my brain into the deep end, drowning me in dizzying puzzles before I’ve even fully read it."
    "Echo un vistazo a la penúltima entrada. Frases clave como \"camino dividido\", \"desvío\" y \"hectáreas de arcos de piedra idénticos\" lanzan mi mente al fondo, ahogándome en rompecabezas mareantes antes de siquiera haberlo leído por completo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s08_7f4bb68c:

    # "Marina peeks over, trying to decipher the entries with me."
    "Marina se asoma por encima, tratando de descifrar las entradas conmigo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:644
translate spanish hwb_s08_4700c8f9:

    # "A speck of inadequacy crawls up inside me and I quickly flip to the next entry before Marina notices I’m stuck."
    "Una pizca de insuficiencia se arrastra dentro de mí y paso rápidamente a la siguiente entrada antes de que Marina note que estoy atascada."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:648
translate spanish hwb_s08_d7b975a3:

    # "I’ll deal with that later. For now, we’ll just narrow this down."
    "Me ocuparé de eso después. Por ahora, solo reduciremos esto."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:658
translate spanish hwb_s08_c646cde7:

    # Marina "You're my Lamasi, Amber!"
    Marina "Ты моя Ламаси, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:663
translate spanish hwb_s08_01d9e930:

    # "Suddenly, my chest feels like a hummingbird is fluttering around in it. I shift my eyes away from her smile and hide my face."
    "De repente, siento como si un colibrí revoloteara dentro de mi pecho. Desvío la mirada de su sonrisa y escondo el rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:665
translate spanish hwb_s08_7e3d4f50:

    # Amber "Thanks…"
    Amber "Спасибо …"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:667
translate spanish hwb_s08_6dc07fe7:

    # "When you strip away the circumstances, I guess I did save and protect her like that Lamasi guy did with the miner."
    "Cuando le quitas las circunstancias, supongo que sí la salvé y protegí, como ese tal Lamasi hizo con el minero."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:671
translate spanish hwb_s08_d2c2042e:

    # Marina "A gorge is like a canyon, right?"
    Marina "Ущелье это то же, что и каньон, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:675
translate spanish hwb_s08_61bdb48b:

    # "Marina leans in closer and points to the entry, strands of her soft hair tickling my cheek. I scoot back and power through it, taking a sharp breath to recollect myself."
    "Marina se inclina más cerca y señala la entrada, unos mechones de su suave cabello me hacen cosquillas en la mejilla. Me echo hacia atrás y sigo adelante, tomando una respiración profunda para recuperarme."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:679
translate spanish hwb_s08_a546032b:

    # Amber "Basically, yeah."
    Amber "В принципе, да."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:686
translate spanish hwb_s08_e31ecd27:

    # "Marina nearly springs out of her seat in a burst of realization, her head an inch away from smacking into the ceiling."
    "Marina casi salta de su asiento en un arranque de comprensión, con la cabeza a un centímetro de golpear el techo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:688
translate spanish hwb_s08_2e827dc4:

    # Marina "Oh my god."
    Marina "Боже мой."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:690
translate spanish hwb_s08_bf343ddc:

    # Marina "Does that mean we get to go to the Grand Canyon? Do we get to go to the Grand Canyon, Amber?"
    Marina "Это значит, что мы едем в Гранд Каньон? Мы едем в Гранд Каньон, Эмбер?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:694
translate spanish hwb_s08_91d09291:

    # Amber "Not unless history decides to rewrite itself."
    Amber "Только если история не решит переписать саму себя."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:698
translate spanish hwb_s08_c8eb5108:

    # Amber "There are lots of canyons with ruins. One of them is the Grand Canyon. But most of them have been cleaned out for hundreds of years."
    Amber "Есть множество каньонов с руинами. И один из них – Гранд Каньон. Но большинство из них обыскивались в течение сотен лет."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s08_4f06afac:

    # "I choke down a groan. Indian ruins aren’t exactly rarities around here. Maybe that other entry wasn’t so bad after all."
    "Reprimo un gemido. Las ruinas indias no son precisamente rarezas por aquí. Quizás esa otra entrada no era tan mala después de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:704
translate spanish hwb_s08_1cc262f9:

    # Amber "So we’re looking for a place that was still being used in the 1850’s."
    Amber "То есть, мы ищем место, которое еще не было заброшено в 1850-х годах."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:708
translate spanish hwb_s08_7efe262b:

    # Marina "Hmm."
    Marina "Хмм."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:710
translate spanish hwb_s08_0bfdd06e:

    # "Marina hunkers down and thinks with me, wrinkles forming on her forehead as she tries to strain out an answer."
    "Marina se agacha y piensa conmigo, formándose arrugas en su frente mientras intenta exprimir una respuesta."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:712
translate spanish hwb_s08_737b25aa:

    # "I’m pretty sure she doesn’t even know where to start, but hey, at least she’s trying."
    "Estoy bastante segura de que ni siquiera sabe por dónde empezar, pero oye, al menos lo intenta."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:716
translate spanish hwb_s08_f7cff455:

    # Amber "Well, there is one place."
    Amber "Ну, есть одно место."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:720
translate spanish hwb_s08_2c42fd59:

    # "Marina hardly gets a breath out before I crush her dreams once again."
    "Marina apenas logra respirar antes de que yo aplaste sus sueños una vez más."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s08_e8d983cd:

    # Amber "Not the Grand Canyon."
    Amber "Не Гранд Каньон."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:730
translate spanish hwb_s08_b8f17b62:

    # "She slinks back into her chair and quietly pouts."
    "Se desliza de vuelta a su silla y hace un puchero en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:734
translate spanish hwb_s08_964da8cc:

    # Amber "It’s still in Arizona, but it’s a different place—Canyon de Chelly."
    Amber "Но это все там же в Аризоне, только место другое – Каньон-де-Шейи."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:736
translate spanish hwb_s08_cf6d3920:

    # Amber "The Navajo weren’t chased out until 1863, so the timing isn’t too screwy."
    Amber "Племя Навахо не было изгнано до 1863, поэтому сроки вполне подходят."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:738
translate spanish hwb_s08_4c6126ec:

    # Amber "Place is loaded with ruins, too."
    Amber "Окрестности также все в руинах."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:742
translate spanish hwb_s08_80785a5d:

    # Marina "Oh, are they Puebloan ruins?"
    Marina "О, это руины племени Пуэбло?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:746
translate spanish hwb_s08_7e9c4746:

    # "My flow of information stops. She knows what I’m talking about? She can actually pronounce it?"
    "Mi flujo de información se detiene. ¿Ella sabe de lo que estoy hablando? ¿De verdad puede pronunciarlo?"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:748
translate spanish hwb_s08_fff7be9f:

    # Amber "Uh… Yeah. I’m surprised you know that."
    Amber "Ээ… Да. Удивлена, что ты знаешь об этом."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:752
translate spanish hwb_s08_94d60e8b:

    # Marina "Yup! I’ve been reading some of those travel guides lying around. Super interesting!"
    Marina "Ага! Я почитала некоторые путеводители, которые здесь валяются. Невероятно интересно!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:754
translate spanish hwb_s08_afdb1737:

    # "Those things must be about as old as I am by now. I didn’t have the heart to throw them away when I was cleaning everything out."
    "Esas cosas deben tener ya casi mi edad. No tuve el corazón para tirarlas cuando estaba limpiando todo."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:758
translate spanish hwb_s08_cf79fd25:

    # Amber "Hey, that’s how I did it. It’s the best way to learn."
    Amber "Вот так я и догадалась. Книги лучший способ, чтобы узнать что-то новое."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:762
translate spanish hwb_s08_67f0382c:

    # Amber "Anyway, Canyon de Chelly is pretty damn close to here."
    Amber "В любом случае Каньон-де-Шейи чертовски близко к нам находится."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:769
translate spanish hwb_s08_8261f6d4:

    # "She gasps."
    "Ella jadea."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:771
translate spanish hwb_s08_f32f2714:

    # Marina "So it might’ve lined up with the route he took!"
    Marina "То есть, это могло бы совпасть с маршрутом, которым путешествовал он!"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:775
translate spanish hwb_s08_e4541be0:

    # Amber "Well, I can’t be one-hundred percent positive, but…"
    Amber "Ну, я не могу быть на сто процентов точной, но …"

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:777
translate spanish hwb_s08_df98c3a6:

    # "I close my eyes and snap the book shut, the air between the pages puffing out at us. Then, with one eye open, shoot Marina a grin."
    "Cierro los ojos y cierro el libro de golpe, el aire entre las páginas nos da una bocanada. Luego, con un ojo abierto, le lanzo una sonrisa a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:781
translate spanish hwb_s08_d07f086e:

    # Amber "I’m pretty sure."
    Amber "Я вполне уверена."

# game/script/hwb_s08.rpy:618
translate spanish hwb_s08_4c354d36:

    # Marina "Relaaaaax. Just figure out where we have to go next."
    Marina "Расслааабься. Просто выясни, куда идти дальше."

